page.title: 10More Yaxham Businesses
page.content: Apart from Farming and the Garden Centre there are many other small business. The following are typical and in most cases only occupy a small amount of space. 1. Car Maintenance and Sales 2. Two Public Houses 3. Welding and Wrought Iron Work 4. Forestry and Forestry Consultancy 5. Office Furniture Warehouse & Sales 6. Large scale egg production units 7. Sign Writer 8. Glazier 9. Several Builders 10.Bicycle Repair and Sales 11 Printer 12.Driving Instructor There are many people living in the area who work in East Dereham or further afield.
